text: TKİ Tavşanlı Linyitspor is a Turkish sports club located in Tavşanlı, Kütahya Province. The football club plays in the Turkish Regional Amateur League. In 2009–2010 season of second league, they promoted to Bank Asya 1.Lig after play-off matches. ==Current squad== ==References== ==External links== *TKİ Tavşanlı Linyitspor on TFF.org Category:Football clubs in Turkey Category:Association football clubs established in 1943 Category:1943 establishments in Turkey
